          {
            "field_id": "pdf:02:programmatic_funding_request:9ae362711857",
            "label": "How will this request benefit the constituents of California's 44th Congressional District?",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Directly supports local aerospace jobs at Opto-Knowledge Systems Inc in Torrance, which holds over $3.6 million in active NASA Science contracts and grants.\n* Funds cutting-edge technical work in the district, including the development of multispectral imaging services and instruments to measure water content on the Moon.\n* Strengthens the local innovation economy through more than $2.7 million in NASA Science obligations flowing to CA-44 entities between FY2023 and FY2025.\n* Inspires the next generation of STEM professionals in the district by involving local firms in high-profile missions like lunar exploration.",
            "rationale": "Cites specific spending data for CA-44, including Opto-Knowledge Systems Inc's $2.1M contract and $1.5M grant for lunar water instrumentation.",
